:

1. *Madam* je bila vrlo uzbuđena. (Madam was very excited.)
2. Ona je sada *madam* u stilu. (She is now a madam in style.)
3. *Madam* je ljubazno odgovorila na moje pitanje. (Madam kindly answered my question.)
4. *Madam*, imam problem sa mojim računarom. (Madam, I have a problem with my computer.)
5. *Madam* je odlučila da poseti svoju sestru. (Madam decided to visit her sister.)